    "variantDecisions": "Variants were carefully chosen for each list item to reflect its functionality and user interaction.  'Trailing' variants include 'Switch', 'Text', 'Arrow', and 'None' to appropriately represent toggle switches, explanatory text, navigation actions, and plain list items, respectively.  'Condition' is set to '1-line' or '2-line' to optimize text display based on content length."
  }
}
